[section#mdspan.sub.extents
    [:en] [`subextents] function
    [:zh_CN] [`subextents] 函数
]

[%@lib subextents]
[codeblock:synopsis]
template<class IndexType, size_t... Extents, class... SliceSpecifiers>
  constexpr auto subextents(const extents<IndexType, Extents...>& src,
                            SliceSpecifiers... raw_slices);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para]
[:en] Let [`slices] be the pack introduced by the following declaration:
[:zh_CN] 令 [`slices] 为以下声明式引入的包组：
[codeblock]
auto [...slices] = canonical_slices(src, raw_slices...);
[codeblock:end]

[para:constraints]
[:en] [`sizeof...(SliceSpecifiers)] equals [`sizeof...(Extents)].
[:zh_CN] [`sizeof...(SliceSpecifiers)] 等于 [`sizeof...(Extents)]。

[para:mandates]
[:en] For each rank index [$k] of [`src]:
[:zh_CN] 对于 [`src] 的每个秩索引：
[list]
[item]
[:en] [`SliceSpecifiers...`[[$k]`]] is a [`submdspan] slice type for [`IndexType], and
[:zh_CN] [`SliceSpecifiers...`[[$k]`]] 为对 [`IndexType] 的 [`submdspan] 切片类型，且
[item]
[:en] [`decltype(slices...`[[$k]`])] is a valid [`submdspan] slice type for the
[$k^\text{th}] extent of [`extents<IndexType, Extents...>].
[:zh_CN] [`decltype(slices...`[[$k]`])] 为 [`extents<IndexType, Extents...>] 的
第 [$k^\text{th}] 个秩的有效 [`submdspan] 切片类型。
[list:end]

[para:expects]
[:en] For each rank index [$k] of [`src], [`slices...`[[$k]`]] is a
valid [`submdspan] slice for the [$k^\text{th}] extent of [`src].
[:zh_CN] 对于 [`src] 的每个秩索引 [$k]，[`slices...`[[$k]`]] 为对 [`src] 的
第 [$k^\text{th}] 个秩的有效 [`submdspan] 切片。

[para]
[:en] Let [`SubExtents] be a specialization of [`extents] such that:
[:zh_CN] 令 [`SubExtents] 为满足以下条件的 [`extents] 的特例：

[list]
[item]
[:en] [`SubExtents::rank()] equals [`[^MAP_RANK](slices, Extents::rank())]; and
[:zh_CN] [`SubExtents::rank()] 等于 [`[^MAP_RANK](slices, Extents::rank())]；以及

[item]
[:en] for each rank index [$k] of [`extents<IndexType, Extents...>] such that
the type of [`slices...`[[$k]`]] is not a collapsing slice type,
[`SubExtents::static_extent([^MAP_RANK](slices, [$k]))] equals the following,
where [$\Sigma_k] denotes the type of [`slices...`[[$k]`]]:
[:zh_CN] 对于 [`extents<IndexType, Extents...>] 的每个秩索引 [$k]，
使得 [`slices...`[[$k]`]] 的类型不是折叠切片类型时，
[`SubExtents::static_extent([^MAP_RANK](slices, [$k]))] 等于下列值，
其中 [$\Sigma_k] 代表 [`slices...`[[$k]`]] 的类型：
 [list]
 [item]
[:en] [`Extents::static_extent([$k])] if [$\Sigma_k] denotes [`full_extent_t]; otherwise
[:zh_CN] 若 [$\Sigma_k] 代表 [`full_extent_t] 则为 [`Extents::static_extent([$k])]；否则

 [item]
[:en] [`[$\Sigma_k]::extent_type::value] if [$\Sigma_k] is a specialization of
[`extent_slice] whose [`extent_type] denotes a specialization of [`constant_wrapper];
[:zh_CN] 若 [$\Sigma_k] 是 [`extent_slice] 的特例，且其 [`extent_type] 代表
[`constant_wrapper] 的特例，则为 [`[$\Sigma_k]::extent_type::value]；

 [item]
[:en] otherwise, [`dynamic_extent].
[:zh_CN] 否则，为 [`dynamic_extent]。
 [list:end]
[list:end]

[para:returns]
[:en] A value [`ext] of type [`SubExtents] such that for each rank index [$k]
of [`extents<IndexType, Extents...>], where the type of [`slices...`[[$k]`]]
is not a collapsing slice type, [`ext.extent([^MAP_RANK](slices, [$k]))]
equals the following, where [$\sigma_k] denotes [`slices...`[[$k]`]]:
[:zh_CN] 一个 [`SubExtents] 类型的值 [`ext]，使得对于 [`extents<IndexType, Extents...>]
的每个秩索引 [$k]，其中 [`slices...`[[$k]`]] 的类型不是折叠切片类型，
[`ext.extent([^MAP_RANK](slices, [$k]))] 等于下列值，其中 [$\sigma_k] 代表 [`slices...`[[$k]`]]：

[list]
[item]
[:en] [`[$\sigma_k].extent] if the type of [$\sigma_k] is a specialization of [`extent_slice],
[:zh_CN] 若 [$\sigma_k] 的类型是 [`extent_slice] 的特例，则为 [`[$\sigma_k].extent]；

[item]
[:en] otherwise, [$U - L], where [=range([$L],[$U])] is the [`submdspan] slice range
of [$\sigma_k] for the [$k^\text{th}] extent of [`src].
[:zh_CN] 否则，为 [$U - L]，其中 [=range([$L],[$U])] 为对 [`src] 的
第 [$k^\text{th}] 个秩的 [`submdspan] 切片范围。
[list:end]
[div:end]
